WEBVTT

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:45.400
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.359
Dried tangerine peel candy from Sister Yuling

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:57.079
Milk candy from Squad Leader Sun

00:00:58.759 --> 00:01:00.280
Sister... Mhm.

00:01:00.280 --> 00:01:02.679
Are we really going to the Cadre School?

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:04.719
Don't you want to go?

00:01:05.079 --> 00:01:07.959
Here, if you get hurt, there's medicine.

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:09.920
If you're cold, there are quilts.

00:01:10.599 --> 00:01:12.359
And lots of candy to eat.

00:01:13.319 --> 00:01:16.200
I'm afraid of meeting bad people in a new place.

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:19.920
Isn't it pretty good for us here?

00:01:20.879 --> 00:01:22.159
Back at the Balu Mansion,

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:23.879
we also thought it was okay.

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.599
If the moldy bread had no maggots, it was edible.

00:01:26.599 --> 00:01:28.519
If the whip didn't break bones,

00:01:28.519 --> 00:01:29.400
we considered ourselves lucky.

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:30.959
But here is different.

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:33.120
How can you compare this to the Balu Mansion?

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.319
It is different.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:36.920
Because the People's Liberation Army

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:37.719
has shown us

00:01:37.719 --> 00:01:39.040
that people can live standing tall.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:42.200
Don't you want to learn to write,

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:43.719
learn to read,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:45.560
and become as capable as Brother Gao Yuan

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:47.799
and Sister Yuling?

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:50.400
They are all so capable.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.760
I can't do it, Sister.

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:55.799
If I just learn a little bit about acupuncture,

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:58.280
I'll feel that's enough.

00:02:03.879 --> 00:02:05.319
Before, at the Balu Mansion,

00:02:05.319 --> 00:02:06.719
we were lambs waiting to be slaughtered.

00:02:07.159 --> 00:02:08.879
Because we escaped,

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:10.240
we became people.

00:02:11.159 --> 00:02:12.280
The next step

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:13.759
is to master skills,

00:02:14.199 --> 00:02:16.000
so we no longer live relying on others' help.

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.879
Only then can we become true,

00:02:17.879 --> 00:02:19.599
independent people who stand tall.

00:02:19.599 --> 00:02:21.199
Do you understand?

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.960
But, Sister...

00:02:24.159 --> 00:02:25.520
I'm scared.

00:02:27.879 --> 00:02:28.840
Don't be afraid.

00:02:29.319 --> 00:02:31.000
Your sister is here.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:32.680
Well...

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:35.280
Sister, I'm willing to go to school.

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:38.080
But you have to teach me to write

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:40.080
"Gesang Deji is not livestock."

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:42.520
Okay, then I'll teach you.

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:44.759
"Gesang Deji is a little greedy cat."

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:47.560
"Gesang Deji is a little lazy pig."

00:02:55.039 --> 00:02:56.840
Actually, I also really want to know,

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:59.400
what kind of place the Cadre School is.

00:02:59.639 --> 00:03:02.039
I heard they give out notebooks and teach literacy there.

00:03:02.199 --> 00:03:03.439
Everything is different.

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:04.840
But I never expected

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:07.639
the first person we'd meet at the Cadre School

00:03:07.879 --> 00:03:09.120
would actually be...

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:10.039
Balu Yundan.

00:03:10.599 --> 00:03:12.520
Aren't those the two traitorous household serfs from your family?

00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:14.080
How are they in the same school as us?

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:16.479
They really delivered themselves right to us.

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.919
Sister, why are they here?

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.479
I heard the Preparatory Committee

00:03:21.879 --> 00:03:24.520
needs to do united front work with Xizang's upper class.

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:26.520
They admitted a group of noble children.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:29.520
I didn't expect Balu Yundan would also...

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:30.439
Let's go.

00:03:32.039 --> 00:03:33.439
Let's grab those two brats and bring them back.

00:03:33.439 --> 00:03:34.319
Flay them alive!

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:35.719
No rush.

00:03:36.039 --> 00:03:37.039
This is Xizang.

00:03:38.039 --> 00:03:39.400
They can't escape my grasp.

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:45.039
Stop slacking, bring the things over.

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:46.039
Mhm.

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:54.120
Sister... Mhm.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.520
Have you ever thought,

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.240
if in the future we have our own house,

00:03:58.319 --> 00:03:59.719
with walls on all sides,

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:01.000
tiles overhead,

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.520
that can shelter us from wind and rain,

00:04:02.719 --> 00:04:05.000
and we can lock the door to keep bad people out?

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.280
If in the future,

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.800
we really have a house of our own,

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.120
just like this room...

00:04:16.279 --> 00:04:17.240
Balu Yundan!

00:04:17.439 --> 00:04:18.720
What are you doing here?

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.519
This time, you delivered yourselves to us.

00:04:29.399 --> 00:04:30.199
Don't come any closer!

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:31.800
Run!

00:04:34.879 --> 00:04:35.720
Balu Yundan!

00:04:36.079 --> 00:04:37.079
Deji and I

00:04:37.079 --> 00:04:38.199
are public servants registered

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:39.720
with the Preparatory Committee.

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:41.399
The PLA sent us here to study.

00:04:41.879 --> 00:04:42.720
Sister!

00:04:44.199 --> 00:04:46.279
What are you doing?!

00:04:46.279 --> 00:04:47.720
Spent a few days with Han soldiers,

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.040
and now you think you're tough?

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.360
Hahaha!

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:53.199
The Sixteen-Article Code of Tibet has been law for centuries.

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:54.720
Its rules are ironclad.

00:04:55.399 --> 00:04:57.319
Those who defy their superiors must be captured.

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:01.319
Even if you flee to the ends of the earth,

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:04.079
I'll drag you back.

00:05:04.319 --> 00:05:06.519
To atone for your sins, circling forever.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.480
What are you doing?!

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:10.279
Let her go!

00:05:11.319 --> 00:05:13.240
Balu Yundan, if you dare touch her,

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.040
I'll fight you to the death!

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.240
Yundan...

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:17.800
These two serf sisters of yours...

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:18.920
This is interesting.

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:21.399
This one's as delicate as a little lamb.

00:05:21.399 --> 00:05:23.399
Look at this one, as fierce as a little leopard.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.720
Yundan,

00:05:26.279 --> 00:05:27.639
Deji is yours.

00:05:27.639 --> 00:05:29.399
Let us brothers have a taste

00:05:29.399 --> 00:05:30.439
of this little leopard, Meiduo.

00:05:36.439 --> 00:05:37.519
Let them go!

00:05:47.439 --> 00:05:48.519
Bullying students?

00:05:49.079 --> 00:05:50.720
Do you want to be expelled?

00:05:50.879 --> 00:05:53.480
We are following the rules passed down by our Tibetan ancestors,

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:56.079
disciplining our own household serfs.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:00.519
Here, there are no nobles,

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:02.319
no household serfs.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:04.759
Only equal students.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.720
If you dare bully students again,

00:06:08.199 --> 00:06:10.160
you are making enemies of the people and the government.

00:06:12.079 --> 00:06:12.839
Now,

00:06:13.319 --> 00:06:14.720
leave this place immediately.

00:06:23.079 --> 00:06:24.519
Let's go.

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:53.439
Student Meiduo,

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:56.759
you suffered before.

00:06:57.920 --> 00:06:59.000
I came to tell you,

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:01.800
after deliberation by the Preparatory Committee for the Tibet Autonomous Region,

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:03.879
Balu Yundan, for drinking, brawling,

00:07:03.879 --> 00:07:05.040
and bullying female students,

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:06.000
with egregious circumstances,

00:07:06.439 --> 00:07:07.600
has been given a major demerit.

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:09.839
If there is a next time,

00:07:10.519 --> 00:07:11.639
he will be expelled directly.

00:07:18.399 --> 00:07:20.319
You would really do this for us serfs

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:22.920
and give a noble's son a demerit?

00:07:23.319 --> 00:07:24.319
Meiduo

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:26.399
Didn't I tell you?

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:28.199
From now on,

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:29.920
there's no distinction between serf and noble.

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:31.959
Everyone is equal.

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.079
Oh, right.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.920
The Preparatory Committee

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:37.439
has also issued a major decision.

00:07:38.079 --> 00:07:40.000
From now on, local governments in Xizang,

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.680
committees, and chieftains

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.720
must not impose

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:44.720
corvée labor on personnel

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:46.199
working for state organs,

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:47.319
or on students and trainees

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.519
in Xizang.
All sectors of society

00:07:48.519 --> 00:07:50.279
should actively support and assist them.

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:51.680
No one

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.600
may persecute them in any form.

00:08:00.519 --> 00:08:01.839
Thank you, Brother Gao Yuan.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:08.199
Thank you, the People's Liberation Army.

00:08:10.839 --> 00:08:12.279
I never thought

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:14.639
we would be protected one day.

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:18.040
The sky of Xizang

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:19.439
is truly changing.

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.600
Meiduo,

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.879
we must keep striving

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:28.319
to ensure all our Tibetan compatriots

00:08:28.879 --> 00:08:30.079
can live equal lives.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:32.519
Mm-hmm.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:36.840
I have a surprise for you.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.080
Your name.

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:41.320
My name?

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:44.840
It's only been a month,

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:45.759
Meiduo.

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:48.320
You're truly amazing.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:51.399
Just like you said,

00:08:51.679 --> 00:08:53.720
I also want all our Xizang compatriots

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.240
to live equal lives.

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:57.879
I'll work even harder.

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.000
Meiduo,

00:09:01.919 --> 00:09:03.000
let me teach you to write.

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:03.879
Okay.

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:07.320
Here.

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:30.480
When he stood before me like a mountain,

00:09:30.919 --> 00:09:32.519
I finally understood.

00:09:32.519 --> 00:09:33.799
Protection isn't possession.

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.279
It's teaching me to stand on my own.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:38.399
During my time at school,

00:09:38.919 --> 00:09:40.799
the pen replaced the shepherd's whip.

00:09:41.279 --> 00:09:42.120
The blackboard erased

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:43.120
the notion of "fate."

00:09:43.879 --> 00:09:45.120
I must study.

00:09:45.399 --> 00:09:46.720
I must study desperately.

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:49.080
I must catch up to Brother Gao Yuan's pace,

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.600
and catch up to my own brand-new destiny.

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:55.399
I learned to write my own name.

00:09:55.919 --> 00:09:58.279
And I will learn much, much more.

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:00.440
For example...

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:01.919
Tomorrow.

00:10:07.879 --> 00:10:08.679
Watch closely now.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:10.399
Start with the left foot.

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:14.360
Left, right, left, kick.

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:16.919
Right foot, left foot.

00:10:16.919 --> 00:10:17.679
Deji, look!

00:10:17.679 --> 00:10:19.120
(Right foot) Brother Gao Yuan messed up again!

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:19.919
Kick!

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.200
Company Commander!

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:24.039
You all should hold hands!

00:10:24.519 --> 00:10:26.200
Oh, right. Okay, come on.

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:29.840
Sister.

00:10:29.840 --> 00:10:30.799
Hmm?

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.679
You mention Brother Gao Yuan every day.

00:10:33.039 --> 00:10:34.720
Who else is in your eyes besides him?

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:35.919
Is there room for anyone else?

00:10:36.399 --> 00:10:38.279
You say his name

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:39.679
ten times more often

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:41.240
than you say mine!

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.279
Am I still your favorite person?

00:10:43.679 --> 00:10:45.279
Of course you're my favorite.

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:48.279
Right, left, right.

00:10:48.279 --> 00:10:50.600
Gao Yuan, your dancing is no good!

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:52.600
Meiduo, Deji!

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:53.879
Stop chatting, you two!

00:10:53.879 --> 00:10:55.200
Come over and teach us!

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:55.879
Okay!

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:57.039
Let's go.

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:04.480
Sister? Hmm?

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:05.279
Go on.

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:07.159
Isn't Brother Gao Yuan over there

00:11:07.159 --> 00:11:08.600
the one who needs a teacher the most?

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:09.399
Go on.

00:11:12.679 --> 00:11:13.480
Attention!

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.919
Come on, classmates, let's all learn together.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.879
Come on.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:21.639
Brother Gao Yuan,

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.080
Guozhuang isn't hard.

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:24.799
Here.

00:11:28.679 --> 00:11:31.000
Left, right, kick.

00:11:31.240 --> 00:11:34.000
Left, right, left, kick.

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:36.480
Right, left, right, kick.

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:38.919
Left, right, left, kick.

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:42.399
Everyone, stop dancing!

00:11:42.519 --> 00:11:44.440
The Central Government has decided on a major contraction of work in Xizang.

00:11:44.639 --> 00:11:46.080
We're all being sent home.